        "### Crafting Formal New Year Greetings for Senior Leaders and HR",
        "When I compose New Year greetings for senior leaders, executives, or members of the HR department, my primary focus is always on demonstrating professionalism, respect, and a keen awareness of their strategic contributions to the organization. These messages are an opportunity to reinforce my commitment to the company's vision and express gratitude for their leadership, not to be overly familiar.",
