        "### Personalizing Colleague New Year Well-Wishes for Different Departments",
        "One of the most effective ways I've found to make New Year wishes truly resonate is by personalizing them for colleagues in different departments. It shows that I understand and appreciate the unique challenges and contributions of their specific roles. It's about demonstrating empathy and a broader organizational perspective.",
        "My process for this involves:",
