        "### Forecasting Positive Outcomes and Shared Goals for 2026",
        "Once I've acknowledged past contributions and expressed gratitude, I always pivot to a forward-looking perspective. The New Year is inherently about new beginnings, and I find it incredibly motivating to infuse my messages with optimism for what's ahead. This isn't about making grand, unrealistic promises, but rather about reinforcing shared purpose and expressing enthusiasm for future collaborations.",
        "My aim here is to connect individual efforts to collective aspirations. We're all part of a larger team striving towards common objectives, and a New Year message is an excellent opportunity to reiterate that shared journey. I often include phrases that look to the future, such as:",
